 and find a rooftop. Wait for the granny to throw some bread. Eat as much bread as possible! BREAD IS LIFE!\n\n\nHow to become the ultimate VR Pigeon:\n\n\u2022 Channel to your inner Pigeon. Bob your head like a pigeon in order to move around and interact with your world\n\u2022 Unlock and discover four different levels\n\u2022 Protect your bread from other pigeons\n\u2022 Use power-ups and map shortcuts to be faster than other pigeons\n\u2022 Your pigeon enemies come in different shapes, avoid unnecessary conflicts!", "short_description": "Bob your head like a pigeon to use the unique movement controls to slip into your pigeon-self!"}]}, "developer_name": "Maestro Pivetta / Studio Seufz", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://vrkiwi.org/what-vr/eula-privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "VRKiwi (MeKiwi)", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://vrkiwi.org/portfolio/vr-pigeons/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1592192974313489"}, {"id": "394813081514456"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ARCADE", "CASUAL", "SIMULATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8169114449820367"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974693_462721473297291_583541181875223647_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=lzFG7QccDgkQ7kNvgGL_J38&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.